text: Zhemgang District is one of the 20 districts in Bhutan. The administrative centre is Zhemgang. Jigme Singye Wangchuck National Park and Royal Manas National Park are both in the district. There are eight village blocks: *Bardho Gewog *Bjoka Gewog *Goshing Gewog *Nangkor Gewog *Ngangla Gewog *Phangkhar Gewog *Shingkhar Gewog *Trong Gewog Category:Districts of Bhutan
title: Zhemgang District
